PHPTracker 0.2.1

PHPTracker is a library suitable to create Bittorrent files of local files,
manage peer announcements and provoding initial seed.

For examples see example_*.php or check http://php-tracker.org/

If you want to use the MySQL persistnce object, see mysql.sql for the table structure.
Tests can be run with PHPUnit, see phpunit.xml for bootstrap configuration.